</h3><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-btwLGw cuLvxI pf-98_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-99_ pf-text-1">Educate employees and individuals on the importance of eye safety and first aid awareness through regular training sessions and informational campaigns.


</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-101_ pf-text-1">Ensure workplaces are equipped with appropriate first aid kits containing eye wash solutions, sterile dressings, and eye patches.



